title: [PS3] Rogero CFW 4.55 v1.00b CEX
description: The latest 4.55 Custom Firmware has been released from developer Rogero. This is a standard CEX CFW with the usual patches found in most CFW's. Rogero already joins the party of 4.55 Standard CEX releases that include ZER0 4.55, Arch 4.55, and FERROX 4.55 CFW's. So the choice is yours as these CFW have basically the same feature sets with a few minor changes in each one. As with ANY CFW release USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. View all the features in this new release from Homebrew & CFW Developer Rogero in the text file.
